---
title: Korean-Style Chicken & Garlic Rice with Veggies, Crushed Peanuts & Fried Egg
description: Are you ready, because when these flavours collide in a sticky mix of sweet chilli, sriracha and sweet soy seasoning, demand for seconds will increase ten-fold. We’re cooking diced chicken in a mouth-watering sauce to blend perfectly with flavourful garlic rice and veggies. Break into the fried egg to really bring this dish into the number one spot of your dinner repertoire.
